    "en": {
      "title": "Urgent message issued by the police regarding 50 people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police have sought the public's help in identifying 50 suspects who broke into Alarmali and damaged property during the anti-government protests.",
        "The Police Media Unit said that investigations will be carried out by the Crime Investigation Unit of the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit.",
        "Police said that if the public has any information about the suspects, they can contact them on 011-2421867, 076-3477342 or 1997. (R)"
      ],
